snippet.title: Agent Awesome Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Are you ready for the most AWESOME videogame you wil EVER experience? Agent Awesome is coming and there is nothing you can do to stop him, the self proclaimed BEST VIDEOGAME IN THE UNIVERSE (Probably also the best one in the Multiverse) will grace your PC, Mac, IOS Device or Android Device real soon.

Is this the BEST trailer in the UNIVERSE or WHAT?! Go and share it! Your father will finally aprove of you when you do it!

Get ready for:
12 levels of PURE AWESOMNESS.
EXPLOSIONS, BULLETS, ACTION, MURDER AND KOALAS !
Deep TACTICAL GAMEPLAY.
Kill everyone...or not! It´s your choice GAMERS LOVE CHOICES!
Lots and lots of WEAPONS and they are UPGRADABLE!
Everything, literally EVERYTHING will make you laugh. WE ARE COOL LIKE THAT!

Find us on:

https://www.facebook.com/ChaosVideogames
https://twitter.com/Game_Brains
http://www.chaosindustries.com.mx/
